        <b>Easier Spot v%1$s</b><br/><br/>
        <b>What is Easier Spot?</b><br/>
        An Android app that shares Wi-Fi hotspot credentials between devices over Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE).<br/><br/>
        <b>Server Mode Requirements:</b><br/>
        • Notifications permission<br/>
        • Shizuku for privileged hotspot access<br/><br/>
